.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div><br />\n仲要預先講定食環報警就出防暴黑警<br />\n你出嘅話個場面實勁過上年"},{"pid":"60df6b0cfb093c102c391baff9680f8a74d39a88","tid":99120,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n仲要預先講定食環報警就出防暴黑警<br />\n你出嘅話個場面實勁過上年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲講到明成班黑警就係等你報警就衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1500警standby緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f6029b2360a4f263ff189f7f10388984fe971e","tid":99120,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"可惜擺多兩年仲會唔會有人記得點解會有得擺，留名睇擺擋日後屌後生仔癈青"},{"pid":"86fc223b99795fd0b34a276dad4202ba99895e49","tid":99120,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"真正既階段性勝利"},{"pid":"3df89f3bd9d1bc1f14b6d1df6108c5139996b327","tid":99120,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暴力換和平<br />\n<br />\n呢句真</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d01710f0eaadc918c2624df32b2bdf2366a0ad","tid":99120,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暴力換和平<br />\n<br />\n呢句真</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56937e06a110e95209a0145bf5f0f755d89ec45e","tid":99120,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"「民以食為天」<br />\n古代中國既起義, 大部份都係因為D人無飯食, 所以起義<br />\n估唔到香港都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雨傘革命D示威者 爭取普選, 但用武力反抗<br />\n反釋法遊行, D示威者反對 破壞香港法律, 但都係無武力反抗<br />\n但年初一無野食, 就馬上武力反抗開拖<br />\n<br />\n由呢件事可以睇到, 想香港出現一場真正革命<br />\n首先要香港人無野食, 就好似黃巾軍, 太平天國, 李自成 都係呢個原因出來起義"},{"pid":"91a16dda23b355e7eecd5e666ba612a7d51dcc13","tid":99120,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:59:59.000Z","msg":"對梁特好失望<br />\n本身搞多次應該血流成河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e89517931583d6bbdc523ff3bee5daf03ed1368","tid":99120,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"小販：多謝警察及特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831cd1e0813f900c8beb9e8a74403f6855cc75cd","tid":99120,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"再次證明以武制暴係有用"},{"pid":"6e835a3fccd63f4f70aacd14c26fe5f306f8eaeb","tid":99120,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afe7215895047c4bbcfe250c8398bddefbdf82b3","tid":99120,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到成班黑警眼光光有得睇冇得食好心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7879ae3d6acbfa48c759f2e8c2789e2e79cd2132","tid":99120,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再次證明以武制暴係有用</blockquote><br />\n每次都係以武制暴係有用<br />\n光復<br />\n碇磚<br />\n<br />\n全部都係做實事"},{"pid":"be31994ceb5ad17ea51b1974f588e3678075bd57","tid":99120,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"<bloc